prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover. A humorous and charming botanical illustration featuring two cartoon capybaras celebrating a birthday. The main capybara, wearing a small, festive party hat askew on its head, is relaxing contentedly in a natural hot spring surrounded by lush, oversized tropical leaves and whimsical, colorful flowers like hibiscus and bird of paradise. Floating in the water around it are several yuzu fruits, one of which has a single, lit birthday candle sticking out of it. A second capybara friend is peeking out from behind a large monstera leaf, smiling and presenting a small, clumsily wrapped gift tied with a simple vine. The overall scene is serene yet comical, with a warm, natural color palette of deep greens, earthy browns, and pops of vibrant floral color. The art style is a flat 2D vector illustration with clean lines and a slightly textured, handcrafted feel. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Hope your birthday is totally chill". The background is a soft, solid off-white color.
